2 HOUSE BILL 519
1 (2) PARAGRAPH (1) OF THIS SUBSECTION APPLIES TO EACH PARKING
2 FACILITY OWNED, OPERATED, OR LEASED BY THE HOSPITAL AT WHICH THE
3 INPATIENT OR OUTPATIENT IS RECEIVING SERVICES.
4 (B) EACH HOSPITAL SHALL DISPLAY SIGNAGE AT EACH PUBLIC ENTRANCE
5 AND PARKING FACILITY INFORMING INPATIENTS AND OUTPATIENTS OF THE
6 AVAILABILITY OF PARKING AT NO COST.
7 SECTION 2. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect
8 October 1, 2025.

